{"id": "rag-005", "scenario": "knowledge", "tags": ["single_turn", "ingredient"], "input": "视黄醇怎么用", "expected": {"routes": ["knowledge"], "task_types": ["knowledge"], "required_tools": ["search_knowledge"], "require_answer": true, "retrieval_grades": {"100016": 2, "100005": 2}, "max_latency_ms": 18000, "ragas_reference": "视黄醇（A醇）是维生素A衍生物，用于抗初老、淡纹、加速角质更新。建议晚间使用，配合防晒；初次使用应从低浓度开始建立耐受，避免同时叠加高浓度酸类。"}}
{"id": "rag-006", "scenario": "knowledge", "tags": ["single_turn", "ingredient"], "input": "维生素C衍生物有什么作用", "expected": {"routes": ["knowledge"], "task_types": ["knowledge"], "required_tools": ["search_knowledge"], "require_answer": true, "retrieval_grades": {"100005": 2}, "reference_answer": "说明维C衍生物美白提亮作用。", "max_latency_ms": 18000, "ragas_reference": "维生素C衍生物（如乙基维生素C）能抑制黑色素生成，起到美白提亮、淡化斑点作用，比纯维C更稳定不易氧化，适合日常护肤使用。"}}
{"id": "rag-007", "scenario": "knowledge", "tags": ["single_turn", "ingredient", "compatibility"], "input": "视黄醇能和维C一起用吗", "expected": {"routes": ["knowledge"], "task_types": ["knowledge"], "required_tools": ["search_knowledge"], "require_answer": true, "reference_answer": "说明两者搭配的注意事项，避免绝对化。", "max_latency_ms": 18000, "ragas_reference": "视黄醇和维C不建议同时使用，尤其早晚同用会互相削弱效果或增加刺激。推荐早上用维C（抗氧化+防晒配合），晚上用视黄醇（抗初老+修护）。"}}
{"id": "rag-008", "scenario": "knowledge", "tags": ["single_turn", "ingredient", "compatibility"], "input": "果酸能和视黄醇一起用吗", "expected": {"routes": ["knowledge"], "task_types": ["knowledge"], "required_tools": ["search_knowledge"], "require_answer": true, "reference_answer": "说明果酸+视黄醇的叠加风险。", "max_latency_ms": 18000, "ragas_reference": "果酸和视黄醇都是活性成分，同时使用会显著增加刺激。建议错开时间（比如隔天）或错开早晚，且必须做好防晒。敏感肌应避免叠加。"}}
{"id": "rag-009", "scenario": "knowledge", "tags": ["single_turn", "ingredient", "restriction"], "input": "孕妇能用视黄醇吗", "expected": {"routes": ["knowledge"], "task_types": ["knowledge"], "required_tools": ["search_knowledge"], "require_answer": true, "reference_answer": "说明视黄醇孕期不建议使用；如知识库无覆盖，如实说明。", "max_latency_ms": 18000, "ragas_reference": "视黄醇孕期不建议使用，可能对胎儿存在潜在风险。孕产妇如需抗初老可选用温和的多肽类或神经酰胺类成分。"}}
{"id": "rag-010", "scenario": "knowledge", "tags": ["single_turn", "ingredient", "compatibility"], "input": "水杨酸和烟酰胺可以同时用吗", "expected": {"routes": ["knowledge"], "task_types": ["knowledge"], "required_tools": ["search_knowledge"], "require_answer": true, "max_latency_ms": 18000, "ragas_reference": "水杨酸和烟酰胺可以搭配使用（都对油皮闭口有帮助），但需注意浓度和肌肤耐受度。建议隔天使用或错开早晚，敏感肌应减少使用频率。"}}
{"id": "rag-011", "scenario": "knowledge", "tags": ["single_turn", "ingredient"], "input": "敏感肌可以用视黄醇吗", "expected": {"routes": ["knowledge"], "task_types": ["knowledge"], "required_tools": ["search_knowledge"], "require_answer": true, "reference_answer": "说明敏感肌需先建立耐受、低浓度尝试。", "max_latency_ms": 18000, "ragas_reference": "敏感肌使用视黄醇需谨慎。建议选低浓度（0.01%-0.1%）产品，先耳后测试，逐步建立耐受，全程加强保湿修护。皮肤急性过敏期暂停使用。"}}
{"id": "rag-012", "scenario": "knowledge", "tags": ["single_turn", "ingredient"], "input": "小棕瓶的核心成分是什么", "expected": {"routes": ["knowledge", "shopping"], "task_types": ["knowledge", "shopping"], "require_answer": true, "retrieval_grades": {"100001": 2}, "max_latency_ms": 18000, "ragas_reference": "雅诗兰黛小棕瓶（特润修护肌活精华露）核心成分是高浓度二裂酵母发酵产物溶胞物，配以透明质酸锁水保湿、猴面包树籽提取物淡纹紧致，主打夜间修护。"}}
{"id": "rag-013", "scenario": "knowledge", "tags": ["single_turn", "usage"], "input": "精华应该在哪一步用", "expected": {"routes": ["knowledge"], "task_types": ["knowledge"], "required_tools": ["search_knowledge"], "require_answer": true, "reference_answer": "说明护肤流程中精华的位置（洁面-爽肤水-精华-乳液-面霜）。", "max_latency_ms": 18000, "ragas_reference": "护肤基础流程：洁面→爽肤水→精华→眼霜→乳液/面霜→防晒（白天）。精华位于爽肤水后、面霜前，遵循\"先水后油、先薄后厚\"。"}}
{"id": "rag-014", "scenario": "knowledge", "tags": ["single_turn", "usage"], "input": "小棕瓶什么时候用效果最好", "expected": {"routes": ["knowledge"], "task_types": ["knowledge"], "required_tools": ["search_knowledge"], "require_answer": true, "retrieval_grades": {"100001": 2}, "reference_answer": "说明小棕瓶主打夜间修护，晚间使用效果更好。", "max_latency_ms": 18000, "ragas_reference": "雅诗兰黛小棕瓶主打夜间修护，建议每晚洁面爽肤后使用。取3-4滴掌心温热，轻按面部至吸收，后续搭配面霜锁养。"}}
{"id": "rag-015", "scenario": "knowledge", "tags": ["single_turn", "usage"], "input": "防晒霜多久涂一次", "expected": {"routes": ["knowledge"], "task_types": ["knowledge"], "required_tools": ["search_knowledge"], "require_answer": true, "reference_answer": "说明每 2-3 小时补涂一次。", "max_latency_ms": 18000, "ragas_reference": "防晒霜建议出门前 15-20 分钟涂抹，每 2-3 小时补涂一次。户外活动、出汗多或涂后擦拭需增加补涂频次。"}}
{"id": "rag-016", "scenario": "knowledge", "tags": ["single_turn", "usage"], "input": "眼霜用多少量合适", "expected": {"routes": ["knowledge"], "task_types": ["knowledge"], "required_tools": ["search_knowledge"], "require_answer": true, "retrieval_grades": {"100016": 2, "100021": 2}, "max_latency_ms": 18000, "ragas_reference": "眼霜用量建议每次一颗黄豆大小（约 0.1-0.2g）。分别取在两侧无名指指腹，从眼下轻按至眼尾，再从眼头轻按至眉尾，避免用力拉扯眼周肌肤。"}}
{"id": "rag-017", "scenario": "knowledge", "tags": ["single_turn", "usage"], "input": "小黑瓶开封后能放多久", "expected": {"routes": ["knowledge"], "task_types": ["knowledge"], "required_tools": ["search_knowledge"], "require_answer": true, "retrieval_grades": {"100002": 2}, "max_latency_ms": 18000, "ragas_reference": "兰蔻小黑瓶等精华类产品开封后建议 6 个月内用完。存放在阴凉干燥处，避免阳光直射；使用前观察是否有变色、异味，如有则停用。"}}
{"id": "rag-018", "scenario": "knowledge", "tags": ["single_turn", "usage"], "input": "卸妆油应该怎么正确使用", "expected": {"routes": ["knowledge"], "task_types": ["knowledge"], "required_tools": ["search_knowledge"], "require_answer": true, "retrieval_grades": {"100017": 2}, "max_latency_ms": 18000, "ragas_reference": "芳珂纳米卸妆油正确用法：干手干脸，取 3-4 泵均匀涂抹全脸打圈按摩 30-60 秒溶解彩妆，加少量水乳化至变白后再洗净。避免湿手湿脸使用（乳化不彻底）。"}}
{"id": "rag-019", "scenario": "knowledge", "tags": ["single_turn", "skin_type"], "input": "干性皮肤应该怎么护肤", "expected": {"routes": ["knowledge"], "task_types": ["knowledge"], "required_tools": ["search_knowledge"], "require_answer": true, "max_latency_ms": 18000, "ragas_reference": "干皮护肤重点：深层保湿、滋润修复。推荐含透明质酸、神经酰胺、角鲨烷、甘油等成分的产品；避免含酒精的控油产品和皂基洁面。护肤流程包括洁面-爽肤水-精华-面霜（可加眼霜）-防晒。"}}
{"id": "rag-020", "scenario": "knowledge", "tags": ["single_turn", "skin_type"], "input": "油皮怎么控油", "expected": {"routes": ["knowledge"], "task_types": ["knowledge"], "required_tools": ["search_knowledge"], "require_answer": true, "retrieval_grades": {"100020": 2, "100006": 2, "100013": 2}, "max_latency_ms": 18000, "ragas_reference": "油皮控油可选含烟酰胺（控油缩毛孔）、锌（辅助控油）或水杨酸（疏通毛孔）的产品。护肤流程精简、避免厚重滋润型面霜，选择清爽水感质地。"}}
{"id": "rag-021", "scenario": "knowledge", "tags": ["single_turn", "skin_type"], "input": "敏感肌屏障受损了怎么办", "expected": {"routes": ["knowledge"], "task_types": ["knowledge"], "required_tools": ["search_knowledge"], "require_answer": true, "retrieval_grades": {"100007": 2, "100012": 2}, "max_latency_ms": 18000, "ragas_reference": "敏感肌屏障受损时应精简护肤、避免刺激成分（果酸、高浓度酸、酒精、香精）。选用含积雪草、马齿苋、神经酰胺、泛醇的修护型产品，重点做好防晒和保湿。"}}
